            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E6%9C%80%E6%9C%89%E5%90%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%92%E8%98%91%E8%8F%87%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%BF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E6%9C%80%E6%9C%89%E5%90%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%92%E8%98%91%E8%8F%87%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%BF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#广东最有名的毒蘑菇即将上线#</span></a><br><br>“吃了白伞伞，回家躺板板”<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>几场雨后，又到了广东人避雷毒蘑菇的季节！<br><br>广东最有名的毒蘑菇就是——致命鹅膏（白毒伞）！同时，致命鹅膏、假褐云斑鹅膏、粉孢牛肝菌、丝盖伞，这4种毒蘑菇在深圳最常见！梧桐山、凤凰山、银湖山和碧岭及周边地区都有它们的“身影”<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>卫子再次提醒，路边的野菇不要采！不要吃！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抓狂]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_zhuakuang-c007ffb7fe.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抓狂]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_zhuakuang-c007ffb7fe.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抓狂]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_zhuakuang-c007ffb7fe.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87V%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87V%E8%